Version 0.1.2 (2009-7-14)
  - Missing key message now tells you what key was missing.
Version 0.1.1 (2009-7-13)
  - Schema defaults are only returned if :default is specified.
  - New class-level DSL for defining schema.
      class Foo < Construct
        define :field, :default => 'zoom'
      end
      Foo.new.field # => 'zoom'
Version 0.1.0 (2009-7-12)
  - First release
